display_long_description:
This is Control Freek, a game about pressing buttons really fast, because sometimes, that’s all you need in life.

We’ll keep working on this game **based on the number of reviews it gets**:

- ~~5 Reviews - Fix bugs (yes, after release).~~  
- ~~9 Reviews - Global leaderboard.~~  
- ~~11 Reviews - Add a trapdoor exit, because why not?~~  
- 23 Reviews - Probably a new level. No promises, but maybe.  
- 42 Reviews - Add an actual menu so things feel more legit.  
- 69 Reviews - A new button. What does it do? We don’t know yet.  
- 99 Reviews - A level with the new button.  
- 112 Reviews - Full level editor, because why build levels ourselves when you can do it for us?

We don’t know how far this game will go. But we’re having fun making it, and if you’re having fun playing it, let us know. Leave a review, push some buttons, and let’s see what happens.

Ohh, btw. Tell us what you think or what you want next here: https://discord.gg/4Zw3jA2T9p
